ompared to HE institutions through one-to-one engagement and discussions with FE colleges, just as they have visited individual HE institutions to discuss Brexit preparedness. While there is no specific mention of visits to FE institutions in the transcripts, it can be inferred that similar engagements are taking place for FE institutions to ensure their readiness for a 'no deal' Brexit scenario.">
